            "text": "Drawn from Day 17 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025) and Week 3 of The Money Journal: 12 Weeks to Peace, Freedom & Overflow (Rebecca J Page, 2025).",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
